headline: Why Lincoln Electric (LECO) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of welding equipment manufacturer Lincoln Electric (NASDAQ:LECO) jumped 4.1% in the afternoon session after the stock's positive momentum continued as the company announced a major partnership with the U.S. Navy and General Dynamics to enhance submarine production, and an analyst raised the stock's price target.
